summary: I haven’t even seen it yet
body:
I haven’t even seen it yet

because I refuse to fork out for yet ANOTHER streaming platform and it’s causing me great emotional anguish, but even the sight of Aziraphale and Crowley in promotional images makes me feel all warm and fuzzy inside.

“There’s my boys! There’s that loser demon and his fusspot angel.” Like some proud, protective mama.

I haven’t met these versions yet but I’d probably kill for them already and that’s kind of sweet!

Aw.

summary: Michael Sheen: We [me and David] were doing an interview yesterday for Good Omens, and the journalist asked me, ‘Were you in a...
caption:
Michael Sheen: We [me and David] were doing an interview yesterday for Good Omens, and the journalist asked me, ‘Were you in a fat suit for it?’, and I’m not! It’s just me! This [gesturing at his back] doesn’t zip up! It’s just me! [To David] Didn’t she?

David Tennant: She did, I’m afraid. She didn’t really recover from that moment.

blog.title: comets weep & leonids fly
blog.description:
Home is where one starts from. As we grow older
The world becomes stranger, the pattern more complicated
Of dead and living. Not the intense moment
Isolated, with no before and after,
But a lifetime burning in every moment
...
Love is most nearly itself
When here and now cease to matter.
--T.S. Eliot, "East Coker"
